{"owner": "Software-Engineering-Spring-2026", "repo": "Polaris.js", "path": "PLAN.md", "message": "plan(req-19): feature decomposition for project CRUD", "content": "# PLAN: Requirement 19 — Student Project Management (CRUD)

## 1. Feature Summary

Requirement 19 enables Students to **Create, View, Update, and Delete projects** with full project details: title, course selection, GitHub link, project report (text), programming languages, demo video, and automatic creation date tracking. The feature is central to the portfolio platform and prerequisite for multiple downstream requirements (20–24, 26, 32, 37–40, 42–46, 59–61, 72). Students access this via the "My Projects" page and a dedicated "Project Editor" modal/page for CRUD operations.

**Related Requirements:** Req 19 (direct); Req 5 (depends on portfolio setup); Req 20–24, 26, 32, 37–41 (depend on Req 19).

---

## 2. Affected Pages & Routes

| Page | Route | Change Type |
|---|---|---|
| My Portfolio | `/portal/student` (sub-tab: Projects) | Modified |
| My Projects | `/portal/student/projects` | New |
| Project Editor | `/portal/student/projects/:projectId?` (modal or sub-page) | New |

---

## 3. New Components to Create

### `ProjectCard` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/ProjectCard.tsx`
```tsx
interface ProjectCardProps {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  course: string;
  languages: string[];
  rating?: number;
  isPublic?: boolean;
  createdDate: string;
  onEdit: (id: string) => void;
  onDelete: (id: string) => void;
  onView: (id: string) => void;
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local (specific to student projects dashboard).
- **Design reference:** Project Explorer cards from `Design/stellar_academic/`; compact summary display with course badge, language chips, action buttons.

### `ProjectEditor` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/ProjectEditor.tsx`
```tsx
interface ProjectEditorProps {
  projectId?: string; // undefined = create new
  onSave: (project: ProjectData) => void;
  onCancel: () => void;
  isLoading?: boolean;
}

interface ProjectData {
  id: string;
  title: string;
  course: string;
  githubLink: string;
  projectReport: string;
  languages: string[];
  demoVideoUrl?: string;
  createdDate: string;
  updatedDate: string;
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local.
- **Design reference:** Form components from styling.md (Input, Textarea, Dropdown, FileUpload); multi-step or single-form layout.

### `ProjectList` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/ProjectList.tsx`
```tsx
interface ProjectListProps {
  projects: ProjectData[];
  onEdit: (id: string) => void;
  onDelete: (id: string) => void;
  onView: (id: string) => void;
  isLoading?: boolean;
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local.
- **Design reference:** Grid or list layout following Polaris spacing tokens.

### `CourseSelector` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/CourseSelector.tsx`
```tsx
interface CourseSelectorProps {
  selectedCourse: string;
  onSelectCourse: (courseId: string) => void;
  disabled?: boolean;
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local or global (if reused in other project-related features).
- **Design reference:** Dropdown from styling.md.

### `LanguageMultiSelect` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/LanguageMultiSelect.tsx`
```tsx
interface LanguageMultiSelectProps {
  selectedLanguages: string[];
  onSelectLanguages: (languages: string[]) => void;
  availableLanguages: string[]; // hardcoded list
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local.
- **Design reference:** Chip/tag selection from styling.md.

### `VideoUploader` — `src/pages/portal/student/projects/components/VideoUploader.tsx`
```tsx
interface VideoUploaderProps {
  videoUrl?: string;
  onVideoUrlChange: (url: string) => void;
  onRemove: () => void;
}
```
- **Reusability:** Page-local (specific to project video).
- **Design reference:** File upload component from styling.md.

---

## 4. Existing Components to Modify

| Component | File | Change Description |
|---|---|---|
| My Portfolio Page | `src/pages/portal/student/portfolio/MyPortfolioPage.tsx` | Add "Projects" tab linking to `/portal/student/projects`. |

---

## 5. State Changes

| Context | New Keys Added | Type | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| (Local Hook) | N/A | See Section 6 | All project state will be encapsulated in a new custom hook `useStudentProjects`. |

---

## 6. New Hooks to Create

### `useStudentProjects`
- **Name:** `useStudentProjects`
- **Location:** `src/pages/portal/student/projects/scripts/useStudentProjects.ts`
- **Returns:**
```tsx
{
  projects: ProjectData[];
  createProject: (project: ProjectData) => void;
  updateProject: (id: string, updates: Partial<ProjectData>) => void;
  deleteProject: (id: string) => void;
  getProjectById: (id: string) => ProjectData | undefined;
  isLoading: boolean;
}
```
- **Data source:** Hardcoded dummy projects array that persists in local component state (not localStorage or Context).

### `useCourses` (if not already global)
- **Name:** `useCourses`
- **Location:** `src/hooks/useCourses.ts` (global, for shared use across features)
- **Returns:**
```tsx
{
  courses: CourseData[];
  getCourseById: (id: string) => CourseData | undefined;
}
```
- **Data source:** Hardcoded list of courses (including "Bachelor Project" special case).

### `useAvailableProgrammingLanguages`
- **Name:** `useAvailableProgrammingLanguages`
- **Location:** `src/hooks/useAvailableProgrammingLanguages.ts` (global)
- **Returns:**
```tsx
{
  languages: string[]; // e.g., ["JavaScript", "TypeScript", "Python", "Java", "React", "Node.js"]
}
```
- **Data source:** Hardcoded list of common programming languages.

---

## 7. Routes to Register

In `src/App.tsx` (or router configuration):

```tsx
{
  path: '/portal/student/projects',
  element: <MyProjectsPage />,
  lazy: () => import('src/pages/portal/student/projects/MyProjectsPage')
}

{
  path: '/portal/student/projects/:projectId',
  element: <ProjectEditorPage />,
  lazy: () => import('src/pages/portal/student/projects/ProjectEditorPage')
}
```

---

## 8. Edge Cases & Error States

### Empty States
- **No projects:** Display empty state message + "Create Project" button.

### Loading States
- Project list loading skeleton while data fetches (if async).

### Error States
- Title required; max 200 characters.
- Course is required.
- GitHub link must be valid URL (optional but if provided, validate).
- Project report (textarea) max 5000 characters.
- At least one programming language required.
- Demo video URL (optional) must be valid URL if provided.
- Video file size max 500MB (if file upload; for now assume URL).

### Deletion Confirmation
- Show confirmation modal before deletion with project title and irreversibility warning.

### Creation Date Tracking
- Automatically set to current date/time on create; immutable thereafter.

### Video URL vs. Upload
- **Scope decision:** For Req 19, support video URL input only (embedded YouTube/Vimeo links). File upload deferred to potential future enhancement.

---

## 9. Open Questions

- [ ] Should the Project Editor be a modal overlay or a separate page route? → **Decision: Separate page route** (`/portal/student/projects/:projectId` for edit, `/portal/student/projects/new` for create).
- [ ] What is the exact format for "project report"? Plain text (textarea) or rich text editor? → **Decision: Plain text textarea** (no Markdown or WYSIWYG for Req 19; can be enhanced later).
- [ ] Video URL: support YouTube/Vimeo embeds only, or generic video file URL? → **Decision: Generic URL for now** (component can embed via `<video>` tag or iframe detection logic later).
- [ ] Should courses be a dropdown or searchable multi-select? → **Decision: Dropdown** (single course per project).
- [ ] Should programming languages be selectable from a fixed list or allow free-text entry? → **Decision: Fixed list of 10–15 common languages** (chips with multi-select).

---

## 10. Checklist (Acceptance Gate)

- [x] All affected requirements listed (Req 19 + dependencies 5, 20–24, 26, 32, 37–41).
- [x] All affected pages/routes listed (My Portfolio, My Projects, Project Editor).
- [x] All new components have props interfaces defined.
- [x] All existing components' changes described (My Portfolio tab).
- [x] All Context/state changes listed (local hook only).
- [x] All new hooks listed with return types (`useStudentProjects`, `useCourses`, `useAvailableProgrammingLanguages`).
- [x] All new routes listed with exact paths.
- [x] All edge cases and error states listed.
- [x] Zero open questions remain (all 4 design decisions documented).

---

## Implementation Priority

1. **Phase 1:** Create `useStudentProjects` hook with dummy data.
2. **Phase 2:** Create `MyProjectsPage` and `ProjectList` component.
3. **Phase 3:** Create `ProjectEditor` component and `ProjectEditorPage`.
4. **Phase 4:** Integrate `CourseSelector`, `LanguageMultiSelect`, `VideoUploader`.
5. **Phase 5:** Wire routing and UI flows.
6. **Phase 6:** Self-review, testing, documentation.

---
"}

